                                            <height atLeast="0.29">0.29</height>
                                            <depth>0.11</depth>
                                        </dimensions>); the back shows anathyrosis at bottom (on a height of 0.075) and top (on a height of 0.03); on the top of the 
                                        fragment, almost above the omicron, the bottom of a dowel hole, combined with the measure of the height, shows that only a small 
                                        part of the block is lost on top.</p>
